  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Supporting Morocco&apos;s prison administration, institution&apos;s and civil society&apos;s ability to respond to emerging and new challenges in line with international human rights standards.</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The project aims to support Morocco&apos;s prisons and civil society to respond to emerging challenges in line with international human rights standards through: 1. Organising training of trainers for prison administration staff on prison management. 2. Organising a round table on the prisons law to bring an international perspective. 3. Providing technical support to the committee in charge of drafting the prison law. 4. Organising a National conference to introduce the new minimum standards for rules for the Treatment of Prisoners.</narrative>
  </description>
